node.text:
Changing the world one smile at a time ❤️

Yesterday @andreamezamx visited @smiletrain’s cleft patient Roberto at home and sat down with his family to learn about his cleft journey. 

For 19 years, Smile Train Mexico’s 37 local partners have supported over 21,000 free cleft surgeries and they continue to provide nutrition, speech, dental and psychosocial cleft care for all those in need 365 days a year. 

To learn more about @smiletrain, visit smiletrain.org 
@smiletrain.la
